  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1017">
<l>nāṇā luyirait tuṟappa ruyirpporuṭṭā</l>
<l>ṉāṇṭuṟavār nāṇāḷ pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The modest would rather lose their life for the sake of modesty than lose modesty for the sake of life.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
